details.description:
Focus on the Road is a solo game about doing a road trip across a huge country. Create a unique character with their interests and beliefs, grab your instant camera and step on the gas. Along your journey you will:
meet interesting people and try to become friends with them;
visit unique places such as impressive natural landmarks, unmissable diners or world famous monuments;
use your instant camera to take stunning pictures of people and landmarks;
try to get enough fuel to continue your road trip unless you like pushing your car in a desert.

What do you need to play?

An eight sided die (1d8) and a four sided die (1d4);
Printed copy of this game or of selected pages (8 printed pages for full experience OR 2 printed pages for compact version). You may also sketch them or take notes on blank paper.
A fuel tank token (a small cube, button, candy, etc);
(obviously) A pen or a pencil;
(optional) A journal if you wish to write down your adventures.Focus on the Road has been created for the Road Trip Game Jam 2025.
